#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/in-ipython.md:1
msgid "_in_ipython"
msgstr "_in_ipython"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/in-ipython.md:3
msgid "Firma"
msgstr "Signature"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/in-ipython.md:9
msgid "Che problema risolve"
msgstr "What problem it solves"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/in-ipython.md:11
msgid ""
"Rileva se il codice sta girando dentro un kernel IPython/Jupyter con "
"display inline disponibile, distinguendolo da una shell terminale o da un"
" ambiente senza IPython."
msgstr "Detects whether the code is running inside an IPython/Jupyter kernel with inline display available, distinguishing it from a terminal shell or an environment without IPython."

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/in-ipython.md:13
msgid "Contratto sugli input"
msgstr "Input contract"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/in-ipython.md:15
msgid "Non richiede argomenti."
msgstr "It takes no arguments."

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/in-ipython.md:16
msgid ""
"Restituisce `True` solo se `IPython` e importabile, esiste una sessione "
"corrente e la configurazione contiene `IPKernelApp`."
msgstr "Returns `True` only if `IPython` is importable, there is a current session, and the configuration contains `IPKernelApp`."

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/in-ipython.md:18
msgid "Dove viene usata"
msgstr "Where it is used"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/in-ipython.md:20
msgid ""
"in [`_style_context`](style-context.md) per decidere se tracciare le "
"figure aperte prima del blocco"
msgstr "in [`_style_context`](style-context.md) to decide whether to track the figures already open before the block"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/in-ipython.md:21
msgid ""
"indirettamente in [`_display_new_figures`](display-new-figures.md) per "
"mostrare solo le nuove figure create nel contesto"
msgstr "indirectly in [`_display_new_figures`](display-new-figures.md) to show only the new figures created inside the context"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/in-ipython.md:23
msgid "Come fallisce"
msgstr "How it fails"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/in-ipython.md:25
msgid ""
"Se `IPython` non e installato oppure non esiste una sessione attiva, "
"restituisce semplicemente `False`."
msgstr "If `IPython` is not installed or there is no active session, it simply returns `False`."

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/in-ipython.md:27
msgid "Perche resta privata"
msgstr "Why it remains private"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/in-ipython.md:29
msgid ""
"E una piccola euristica infrastrutturale specifica del comportamento dei "
"notebook, utile internamente ma poco significativa come API pubblica."
msgstr "It is a small infrastructural heuristic specific to notebook behaviour, useful internally but not very meaningful as a public API."

